<DATELINE>NASHVILLE, Tenn. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Country music star Johnny Cash, honored
for his songwriting achievements, says his songs are as dear as
family members.
   Cash received the Aggie Award on Wednesday night from the
Songwriters Guild of America. He became the 18th recipient of the
award, joining other composers like Sammy Cahn, Johnny Mercer and
Henry Mancini.
